    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/f52facf88053bb578e21c33a8e9cacfe.poster.avif?t=1755346357\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/f52facf88053bb578e21c33a8e9cacfe.webm?t=1755346357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/f52facf88053bb578e21c33a8e9cacfe.mp4?t=1755346357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>数字工厂是一款开放式工厂与自动化游戏，融合数学机制。设计、建造并优化工厂，实现复杂数值结构的自动组装与交付。灵感源自Opus Magnum与Infinifactory。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/1decd0c41da41a3a0092429e2abe7c8b.poster.avif?t=1755346357\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/1decd0c41da41a3a0092429e2abe7c8b.webm?t=1755346357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/1decd0c41da41a3a0092429e2abe7c8b.mp4?t=1755346357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在六边形网格上使用专用机器建造完全自动化的工厂。通过数学运算移动、组合、分割、摧毁和修改编号球体，以形成具有特定形状和数值的所需结构。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/a2cb973834f1ee8a51ba24b626e866f7.poster.avif?t=1755346357\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/a2cb973834f1ee8a51ba24b626e866f7.webm?t=1755346357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/a2cb973834f1ee8a51ba24b626e866f7.mp4?t=1755346357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>使用传送带、推杆、激光、磁铁、旋转器等多种设备，打造高效的系统。通过优化尺寸和速度，攀登排行榜... 但要小心：一个小小的疏忽，整个设计都可能失败！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/950fc86770ee7f6d8fa0d8d1dff1b2a3.poster.avif?t=1755346357\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/950fc86770ee7f6d8fa0d8d1dff1b2a3.webm?t=1755346357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231090/extras/950fc86770ee7f6d8fa0d8d1dff1b2a3.mp4?t=1755346357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏采用独特的细胞着色艺术风格，呈现出色彩鲜艳、简洁明快且充满风格化的视觉效果。所有动画过渡自然流畅，从开始到结束采用单一连续的摄像机运动，让玩家全程沉浸其中。</p>",
